<p>Please do not tout or get LASIK before you read
http://www.lasikeyesurgerywebsite.com/Ten%2520Reasons.pdf</p>

<p>I&#8217;ve been in the vision research business for over 40 years and beg you not to let them shave your eyeballs.</p>

